EN: I bought a new chair and put it in the living room.

ZH: 这个凳子很舒服，你可以试试。
EN: This chair is very comfortable, you can try it.

ZH: 她把凳子放在书桌前面。
EN: She put the chair in front of the desk.

ZH: 这个凳子有点儿高，我坐不好。
EN: This chair is a bit high, I can't sit comfortably.

ZH: 这个凳子的背部设计得很好，对腰部非常有支撑。
EN: The backrest of this chair is designed very well, providing great support for the waist.

ZH: 我终于找到了一把和我的桌子配套的凳子。
EN: I finally found a chair that matches my desk.

ZH: 他把凳子往后移了一些，给我腿部更多的空间。
EN: He moved the chair back a little to give me more legroom.

